   Category: Children and Youth

   Children and youth are the hope of our future. The sites included here
   are intended to provide information necessary for children and youth
   with disabilities to reach their full potential.

   The Administration will work to ensure that all Americans have the
   opportunity to learn and develop skills, engage in productive work,
   choose where to live and participate in community life. New Freedom
   Initiative

